en_123251_0	The number of workers hospitalized by food poisoning in a garment factory in Allawarawa, balangoda has risen up to 300 while many others with similar symptoms are being taken to the hospital, a correspondent from Balangoda hospital said to Hiru News.
en_123251_1	The breakfast provided by the Garment factory today has been poisonous to the hospitalized workers.
en_123251_2	Many others who exhibit similar symptoms are being admitted to Balangoda hospital.
en_123251_3	Balangoda Police station investigates the incident.
